Description: The Data.BaltimoreCity.Gov Vegetated Area API returns esriGeometryPolygon data with vegetated zones in the city of Baltimore. Supported Query Formats: JSON, AMF, geoJSON. See a live example at https://data.baltimorecity.gov/dataset/Vegetated-Area-egis_rest_services_OpenBaltimore_Ve/jraa-fcme This API is provided by OpenBaltimore, Baltimore City's Open Data Warehouse.
